*Ljudima* se obično može verovati (People can usually be trusted).
*Ljudima* se priča da će dobiti nova odelenja (People are being told they will get new departments).
*Iskustva su pokazala da *ljudima* to ne odgovara (Experience has shown that it does not suit people).
*Koristimo tehnologiju da olakšamo *ljudima* posao (We use technology to make people's work easier).